      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You have to see this beauty in person to believe it. It\u2019s seriously like it just rolled off the showroom floor\u2014absolutely flawless inside and out! I\u2019ve babied this car since day one, and it still has that fresh feel and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically brand new but without the brand-new price tag, this is definitely the one for you. Drop me a message and come take it for a spin!",
