    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a superlative 996.2 Carrera 4S in museum-grade condition. This example features the M96 3.6L flat-six engine with a documented IMS bearing retrofit and rear main seal replacement. The 6-speed G96 transaxle provides crisp engagement, distributing power through the viscous-coupling AWD system. The wide-body chassis remains perfectly true, supported by a factory-spec suspension with zero bushing play or strut leakage. Braking is handled by four-piston monobloc calipers over ventilated, cross-drilled rotors with no heat checking. The finish maintains factory paint depth with no evidence of oxidation or clear-coat failure. A mechanically sorted, turn-key investment for the discerning purist.",
      "price": 44800.0,
