    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional example of automotive preservation. This vehicle remains in showroom-quality condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior paint retains its deep, original luster, protected by a professional-grade ceramic coating; there are absolutely no rock chips, dings, or swirl marks to be found. Inside, the premium leather upholstery is pristine, showing no signs of side-bolster wear or creasing, and it still carries that distinctive new-car scent. Every electronic component, from the high-fidelity sound system to the ambient lighting and navigation, functions flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, backed by a comprehensive chronological folder of every service record performed exclusively at the original dealership. It has never been driven in inclement weather, and the undercarriage is as clean as the bodywork. This is a rare opportunity for a discerning collector or enthusiast to own a vehicle that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line.",
